name: The 7 Talisman of Work: Wrench
description:
Every warriors sheath has known of the essential powers of this tool.
Forged from the purest silver. Hallmarked so you will know it's maker.
This is more of a jewel in a crown.
The crown of a working tribe.
The notion of its existence is a rare one.
The importance of it is the only known truth.
